project_descr: UN and UNDP Response to Tropical Storm Ketsana (locally named Ondoy) - This programme seeks to strengthen the capacities of UNCO and UNDP to respond effectively to early recovery needs arising from the damages caused by Tropical Storm Ketsana.

outputs.output_descr: Supports strengthening of Resident Coordinator functions, conduct of multi-sectoral assessment and enhancement of UNDP Philippines capacity to lead the early recovery cluster

project_title: un and undp response to tropical storm ketsana
